d\n \ninfrastructure,\n \nsoftware,\n \nand\n \nservices\n \nfor\n \ndeploying\n \nLlama\n \nmodels.\n  \nLlama  4  Maverick  \n Llama  4  Maverick  is  a  Mixture-of-Experts  (MoE)  model  with  17  billion  active  parameters  and  128  experts.   \n"
